{"data":[{"date":"14:49 01/08","title":"Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ea1o ra c\u00fa s\u1ed1c v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Argentina","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/chelsea-san-sang-tao-ra-cu-soc-vu-gonzalo-higuain.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Gonzalo Higuain c\u1ee7a Juventus, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t AC Milan trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">AC Milan ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n Higuain</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo khi\u1ebfn Higuain kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ra \u0111i, anh kh\u00f4ng quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m l\u00e0m n\u1ec1n cho si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3. AC Milan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111ang chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u1ee5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t AC Milan, Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Gonzalo Higuain v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t AC Milan, Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Gonzalo Higuain v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/Vuot-mat-AC-Milan,-Chelsea-muon-mua-Gonzalo-Higuain-voi-gia-khung-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>AC Milan \u0111ang chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u1ee5 Gonzalo Higuain</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00f4m qua, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0a tin AC Milan \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Gonzalo Higuain. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3 16 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a sau \u0111\u00f3 k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 36 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 ng\u00e0y, t\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Milan m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp 3 b\u00ean gi\u1eefa ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Higuain, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Leonardo c\u1ee7a AC Milan v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t quan ch\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Juventus \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c. B\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n Higuain \u0111\u00e3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-italia/juventus-len-tieng-vu-ban-higuain-cho-ac-milan-176-192462.html\" target=\"_blank\">Juventus ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn Higuain t\u1edbi AC Milan</span>. Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Giuseppe Marotta c\u1ee7a Juventus kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cCh\u01b0a c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00fd k\u1ebft c\u1ea3, Higuain v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Juventus\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t AC Milan v\u1ee5 Higuain</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 AC Milan v\u1eabn \u0111ang trong th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Higuain, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. Khi m\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c th\u00f4ng qua th\u00ec c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ea1o ra c\u00fa s\u1ed1c v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ea1o ra c\u00fa s\u1ed1c v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/chelsea-san-sang-tao-ra-cu-soc-vu-gonzalo-higuain.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t AC Milan v\u1ee5 Higuain</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Gonzalo Higuain c\u1ee7a Juventus, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t AC Milan trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo The Sun, Chelsea t\u00ednh ch\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ee7 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, h\u1ecd \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u1eb7ng \u0111\u00f4 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJuventus kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n thu v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t t\u1eeb Higuain, l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb Chelsea t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n vi\u1ec7c nh\u1eadn 2 l\u1ea7n ti\u1ec1n t\u1eeb AC Milan.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Higuain \u1edf Stamford Bridge, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Chelsea mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i, Morata ho\u1eb7c Giroud s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1880","checkdouble":"192472"},{"date":"14:46 01/08","title":"Sao M.U: \"HLV Mourinho \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/sao-mu-hlv-mourinho-dang-rat-hanh-phuc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid trong tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ander Herrera chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Jose Mourinho v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t tinh th\u1ea7n ph\u1ea5n ch\u1ea5n.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nHerrera cho bi\u1ebft Mourinho \u0111ang r\u1ea5t l\u1ea1c quan<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tour du \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda c\u1ee7a Man United, khi h\u1ecd thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t v\u00ec nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do kh\u00e1c nhau. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn trong ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1eefa Mourinho v\u00e0 Ed Woodward c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, khi h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t t\u00e2n binh Fred l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u00e1nh n\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n che tan m\u00e2y m\u00f9 c\u1ee7a M.U, ngay sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid. HLV Mourinho t\u1ecf ra h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c khi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111ang d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2 cho M.U &ndash; Herrera cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3. HLV \u0111ang r\u1ea5t l\u1ea1c quan, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y t\u1ecf ra h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u00f4ng \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu. Jose h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n ti\u1ec1n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Herrera chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Jose Mourinho\" title=\"Herrera chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Jose Mourinho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/sao-mu-hlv-mourinho-dang-rat-hanh-phuc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Herrera chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Jose Mourinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh cho m\u1ecdi danh hi\u1ec7u. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu HLV mu\u1ed1n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1ea5y v\u1edbi BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.&rdquo;&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda t\u00f4i, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c cho Man United trong m\u1ed7i bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp, trong m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. Sau \u0111\u00f3, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi CLB v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn, n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u khi b\u1ea1n ch\u01a1i cho 1 trong 5 CLB h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00e0ng l\u00e2u c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Herrera chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Jose Mourinho, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft &ndash; 9 ng\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Leicester City.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-chia-se-ve-luc-luong-mu-thua-nhan-khong-biet-martial-o-dau-172-192459.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/mourinho-chia-se-ve-luc-luong-mu-thua-nhan-khong-biet-martial-o-dau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-chia-se-ve-luc-luong-mu-thua-nhan-khong-biet-martial-o-dau-172-192459.html\">Mourinho chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U, th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft Martial \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u</span><br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, Mourinho chia s\u1ebb t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin vui bu\u1ed3n tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-mu-21-real-madrid-icc-2018-329-192449.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/video-tong-hop-mu-21-real-madrid-icc-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-mu-21-real-madrid-icc-2018-329-192449.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: MU 2-1 Real Madrid (ICC 2018)</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i ICC 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Real Madrid, HLV Jose Mourinho b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh, \u00edt thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 trong tr\u1eadn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1879","checkdouble":"192473"},{"date":"16:00 01/08","title":"Valverde \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean t\u00e2n binh tai ti\u1ebfng c\u1ee7a Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/hlv-valverde-khen-ngoi-malcom.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Javier Pastore ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar, c\u1ef1u sao PSG kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi PSG \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Neymar b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, PSG chi 222 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar t\u1eeb Barca. D\u00f9 m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Javier Pastore ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Javier Pastore ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/15/Javier-Pastore-phat-bieu-ve-Neymar-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Neymar c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi PSG \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNeymar \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed, m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Cavani v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c NHM \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-muon-mua-neymar-gia-350-trieu-euro-180-188122.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Neymar</span>, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil thay Ronaldo, ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eeba k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Juventus. Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 290 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu Neymar.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pastore kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Neymar kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi PSG</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Javier Pastore ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar, c\u1ef1u sao PSG kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi PSG \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar PSG\" title=\"Neymar PSG\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/17/dong-doi-tiet-lo-tuong-lai-neymar.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pastore kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Neymar kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi PSG</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNeymar s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi PSG \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. PSG \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0o c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. H\u1ecd d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o Neymar r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y d\u00ednh\u00a0ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 l\u1ee1 m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, nh\u01b0ng m\u00f9a t\u1edbi m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cNeymar \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh sau khi ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf World Cup 2018, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Neymar s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNeymar ghi 19 b\u00e0n sau 20 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Ligue 1 m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, anh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Edinson Cavani v\u00e0 Kylian Mbappe h\u1ee3p th\u00e0nh b\u1ed9 ba si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p. Song v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 2 n\u0103m nay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 h\u1ebft m\u00f9a.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i khi\u1ebfn Neymar kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup 2018, anh ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 Brazil b\u1ecb B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1878","checkdouble":"192474"},{"date":"16:26 01/08","title":"Thi\u1ebfu th\u1ed1n nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1, HLV Tottenham chuy\u1ec3n sang s\u00e0i \u201ch\u00e0ng nh\u00e0\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/hlv-pochettino-hua-trao-co-hoi-cho-cau-thu-tre-tottenham.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Pochettino h\u1ee9a trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Tottenham. \u00d4ng \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng h\u1ecd t\u1ea1i Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pochettino \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Tottenham t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ho\u1eb7c v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t do m\u1edbi d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV Mauricio Pochettino v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTottenham \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng 2 trong s\u1ed1 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qua t\u1ea1i International Champions Cup. H\u1ecd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Roma 4-1, th\u1eafng Milan 1-0 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 thua Barca tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m sau khi h\u00f2a 2-2 \u1edf th\u1eddi gian ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c. Th\u00f4ng qua \u0111\u00f3, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, HLV Pochettino h\u1ee9a trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Tottenham trong m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Pochettino h\u1ee9a trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Tottenham h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Pochettino h\u1ee9a trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Tottenham h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/HLV-Pochettino-hua-trao-co-hoi-cho-cau-thu-tre-Tottenham-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pochettino h\u1ee9a trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Tottenham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTh\u1eadt ti\u1ebfc khi thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7\u201d, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina n\u00f3i sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc AC Milan. \u201cNh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui v\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng nhau v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng CLB l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 Roma, Barcelona v\u00e0 Milan. Th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i 1. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ch\u00fac m\u1eebng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c HLV \u1edf h\u1ecdc vi\u1ec7n. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u1eadt l\u1ef1c trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u0111\u00f3 cho \u0111\u1ed9i 1.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1edbi l\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tottenham vs Milan\" title=\"Tottenham vs Milan\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/hlv-pochettino-hua-trao-co-hoi-cho-cau-thu-tre-tottenham.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Luke Amos l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \"m\u1ea7m non\" Spurs t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPochettino n\u00f3i th\u00eam: \u201cSau 4 n\u0103m, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i lo s\u1ee3 khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb? H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao, nh\u01b0ng b\u00f9 l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 kh\u00e1t khao v\u00e0 n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0 Harry Kane v\u00e0 Christian Eriksen khi c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c h\u1eadu b\u1ed1i \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf tour du \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cGi\u1edd th\u00ec sao? Sau 4 n\u0103m, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu tin v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, \u0111\u1eebng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn kinh nghi\u1ec7m. B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m, t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, l\u00e0 t\u00ednh chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p. L\u1ea5y v\u00ed d\u1ee5 Luke Amos ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i g\u1ea7n tr\u1ecdn c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Tottenham tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tottenham-vs-ac-milan-07h30-ngay-18-tran-dau-icc-2018-372-192426.html\">Tottenham 1-0 AC Milan (KT): Rossoneri b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn v\u00ec d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ec7 v\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tottenham-phai-mua-kondogbia-gia-70-trieu-bang-172-192400.html\">Tottenham nh\u1eadn b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 kh\u1ee7ng d\u00e0nh cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u01a1 b\u1eafp</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-pochettino-phat-bieu-ve-chuyen-nhuong-tottenham-172-192372.html\">V\u00ec c\u00e2u n\u00f3i n\u00e0y, Pochettino khi\u1ebfn C\u0110V Tottenham lo ngay ng\u00e1y</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pochettino-khang-dinh-khong-mua-lai-gareth-bale-172-192272.html\">Pochettino kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng mua l\u1ea1i Gareth Bale</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1877","checkdouble":"192475"},{"date":"15:38 01/08","title":"3 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1eaft gi\u1ea3m k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9, t\u1eadp trung s\u1edbm c\u00f9ng MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/3-tru-cot-cat-giam-ky-nghi-tap-trung-som-cung-mu.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh MU v\u1eeba nh\u1eadn tin vui t\u1eeb Romelu Lukaku, Marcus Rashford v\u00e0 Phil Jones, Mourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u1eaft gi\u1ea3m k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung s\u1edbm c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n, song Mourinho \u0111ang g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a M.U l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 3 tu\u1ea7n, nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung mu\u1ed9n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh MU \u0111\u00f3n tin m\u1eebng t\u1eeb 3 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh MU \u0111\u00f3n tin m\u1eebng t\u1eeb 3 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Doi-hinh-MU-don-tin-mung-tu-3-tru-cot-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng Marouane Fellaini, Romelu Lukaku, Phil Jones, Ashley Young, Jesse Lingard, Marcus Rashford v\u00e0 Paul Pogba s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung mu\u1ed9n c\u00f9ng M.U, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Leicester v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh MU \u0111ang v\u1eafng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Valencia, Smalling v\u00e0 Matic \u0111ang g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00e1c nhau, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Leicester v\u1eabn \u0111ang b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho \u0111ang m\u1ea5t qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng thu v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u01b0ng \u00fd, chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>3 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u1edbm h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh MU v\u1eeba nh\u1eadn tin vui t\u1eeb Romelu Lukaku, Marcus Rashford v\u00e0 Phil Jones, Mourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u1eaft gi\u1ea3m k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung s\u1edbm c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lukaku\" title=\"Lukaku\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/Jose-Mourinho-phat-bieu-ve-Romelu-Lukaku-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lukaku tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u1edbm h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cLukaku, Rashford v\u00e0 Jones \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eaft gi\u1ea3m k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung s\u1edbm c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Lindelof. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9\u00a0 Romelu Lukaku, Marcus Rashford v\u00e0 Phil Jones c\u1eaft gi\u1ea3m k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9, song kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Leicester hay kh\u00f4ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho v\u1eabn \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n mua m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. Hi\u1ec7n Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham v\u00e0 Harry Maguire l\u00e0 2 \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1876","checkdouble":"192478"},{"date":"16:00 01/08","title":"\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Neymar","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/17/dong-doi-tiet-lo-tuong-lai-neymar.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Javier Pastore ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar, c\u1ef1u sao PSG kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi PSG \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Neymar b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, PSG chi 222 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar t\u1eeb Barca. D\u00f9 m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Javier Pastore ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Javier Pastore ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/15/Javier-Pastore-phat-bieu-ve-Neymar-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Neymar c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi PSG \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNeymar \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed, m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Cavani v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c NHM \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-muon-mua-neymar-gia-350-trieu-euro-180-188122.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Neymar</span>, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil thay Ronaldo, ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eeba k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Juventus. Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 290 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu Neymar.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pastore kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Neymar kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi PSG</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Javier Pastore ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar, c\u1ef1u sao PSG kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi PSG \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar PSG\" title=\"Neymar PSG\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/17/dong-doi-tiet-lo-tuong-lai-neymar.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pastore kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Neymar kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi PSG</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNeymar s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi PSG \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. PSG \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0o c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. H\u1ecd d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o Neymar r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y d\u00ednh\u00a0ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 l\u1ee1 m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, nh\u01b0ng m\u00f9a t\u1edbi m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cNeymar \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh sau khi ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf World Cup 2018, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Neymar s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNeymar ghi 19 b\u00e0n sau 20 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Ligue 1 m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, anh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Edinson Cavani v\u00e0 Kylian Mbappe h\u1ee3p th\u00e0nh b\u1ed9 ba si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p. Song v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 2 n\u0103m nay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 h\u1ebft m\u00f9a.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i khi\u1ebfn Neymar kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup 2018, anh ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 Brazil b\u1ecb B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1875","checkdouble":"192479"},{"date":"17:04 01/08","title":"HLV Lopetegui n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n Real mu\u1ed1n mua Courtois?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/15/hlv-lopetegui-phat-bieu-ve-viec-real-mua-courtois.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Julen Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Real mua Courtois. T\u00e2n HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Los Blancos t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 Courtois hay b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real nh\u1eafm Courtois thay Navas</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong v\u00e0i n\u0103m qua, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i thay th\u1ebf Keylor Navas. N\u0103m 2015, su\u00fdt n\u1eefa Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 David De Gea t\u1eeb Man United n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecfng m\u00e1y fax hy h\u1eefu t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1eddi gian tr\u00f4i qua, M.U v\u1eabn d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu nh\u1ea3 De Gea. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Real ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 Alisson hay Thibaut Courtois. Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft, Alisson \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn Liverpool l\u00e0m b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi v\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u1ea3 d\u0129 nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi Real l\u00e0 Courtois.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Real mua Courtois h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Real mua Courtois h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/15/hlv-lopetegui-phat-bieu-ve-viec-real-mua-courtois.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u00f3 tin Real mu\u1ed1n mua Courtois thay Navas</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Courtois v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m n\u1eefa l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n. C\u00f3 tin Real s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 35 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 mua l\u1ea1i giao k\u00e8o c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Lopetegui t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Real mang v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb Andriy Lunin t\u1eeb Zorya (Ukraine). C\u1ed9ng th\u00eam Keylor Navas l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n s\u1ed1 1 trong v\u00e0i n\u0103m qua v\u00e0 Kiko Casilla, HLV Julen Lopetegui c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111ang t\u1ed1n nhi\u1ec1u gi\u1ea5y m\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a b\u00e1o ch\u00ed.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lopetegui ra mat CLB Hoang gia sau khi bi sa thai\" title=\"Lopetegui ra m\u1eaft CLB Ho\u00e0ng gia sau khi b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/real-madrid-se-chieu-mo-cau-thu-nao-sau-khi-chia-tay-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Real mua Courtois</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd b\u00e0n v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf Real Madrid\u201d, Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Real mua Courtois khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp. \u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u00f3 v\u00e0 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u00e1ng nay, Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real khi h\u1ecd th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man United \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Kiko Casilla v\u00e0 Andriy Lunin m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1eaft m\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7p cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/real-nham-2-sao-khung-nhat-ngoai-hang-anh-nang-cap-hang-cong-172-192466.html\">Real nh\u1eafm 2 sao kh\u1ee7ng nh\u1ea5t Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-co-150-trieu-euro-cung-dung-mo-lewandowski-180-192443.html\">Real Madrid c\u00f3 150 tri\u1ec7u Euro c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eebng m\u01a1 Lewandowski</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/clb-real-madrid-co-dong-thai-moi-vu-hazard-180-192441.html\">CLB Real Madrid c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i m\u1edbi v\u1ee5 Hazard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tu-bo-hazard-real-chi-70-trieu-euro-mua-sao-khung-dortmund-180-192424.html\">T\u1eeb b\u1ecf Hazard, Real chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro mua sao kh\u1ee7ng Dortmund</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/co-hay-khong-viec-real-chi-70-trieu-bang-mua-willian-180-192421.html\">C\u00f3 hay kh\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c Real chi 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Willian?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1874","checkdouble":"192483"},{"date":"17:28 01/08","title":"HLV Roma c\u1ea1n l\u1eddi khi nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi c\u00e1i t\u00ean Malcom","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/hlv-di-francesco-phat-bieu-ve-vu-roma-mua-hut-malcom.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Di Francesco ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 Roma mua h\u1ee5t Malcom. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 48 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec kh\u00e1c khi m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil ch\u1ecdn Barcelona ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>C\u1ea1n l\u1eddi v\u1edbi Malcom</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAS Roma \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t t\u00e2n binh trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 Robin Olsen, Javier Pastore v\u00e0 Justin Kluivert. \u1ede chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Giallorossi \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0 Radja Nainggolan v\u00e0 Alisson ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00fang ra Roma \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 th\u00eam t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Malcom t\u1eeb Bordeaux. \u0110\u00f4i b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf, ra m\u1eaft cho Malcom. Nh\u01b0ng b\u1ed7ng ch\u1ed1c, c\u1ea3 Bordeaux v\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec1u \u201cl\u1eadt k\u00e8o\u201d tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn c\u1ee7a Barcelona.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Di Francesco ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 Roma mua h\u1ee5t Malcom h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Di Francesco ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 Roma mua h\u1ee5t Malcom h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/HLV-Di-Francesco-phat-bieu-ve-vu-Roma-mua-hut-Malcom-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Malcom \u0111\u00e3 \"l\u1eadt k\u00e8o\" v\u1edbi Roma \u0111\u1ec3 sang Barca</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Eusebio Di Francesco ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 Roma mua h\u1ee5t Malcom. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn khi m\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Brazil \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn Barca l\u00e0m b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh th\u1ea3n. N\u1ebfu Barcelona mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Malcom, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng. T\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i c\u00f3. N\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn Barcelona, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec kh\u00e1c\u201d, Di Francesco n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Roma Di Francesco\" title=\"HLV Roma Di Francesco\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/hlv-di-francesco-phat-bieu-ve-vu-roma-mua-hut-malcom.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Di Francesco ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 Roma mua h\u1ee5t Malcom</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Roma ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 Malcom, HLV Di Francesco cho bi\u1ebft c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Roma m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t. \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ph\u00ecnh to\u201d, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Roma n\u00f3i th\u00eam. \u201cGi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Monchi c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u00d4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1 \u0111ang \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n. C\u00f2n t\u00f4i, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n qu\u00e2n s\u1ed1 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 30 ng\u01b0\u1eddi. t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 AS Roma tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/barca-vs-roma-tran-dau-icc-2018-372-192427.html\">Barca 2-4 Roma (KT): M\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Giallorossi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-hang-hot-bailey-172-192291.html\">Chelsea c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 h\u00e0ng hot Bundesliga</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/roma-nhan-barca-muon-bo-qua-vu-malcom-vay-dua-messi-day-184-192094.html\">Roma nh\u1eafn Barca: \u201cMu\u1ed1n b\u1ecf qua v\u1ee5 Malcom, v\u1eady \u0111\u01b0a Messi \u0111\u00e2y\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/malcom-chia-khoa-cho-su-linh-hoat-cua-barcelona-180-192062.html\">Malcom \u2013 Ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a cho s\u1ef1 linh ho\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Barcelona</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/roma-chuan-bi-khoi-kien-bordeaux-vi-lat-keo-vu-malcom-184-191956.html\">Roma chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u1edfi ki\u1ec7n Bordeaux v\u00ec l\u1eadt k\u00e8o v\u1ee5 Malcom</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1873","checkdouble":"192485"},{"date":"17:16 01/08","title":"Fabinho v\u00e0 Naby Keita: Tr\u00e1i tim c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/fabinho-va-naby-keita-trai-tim-cua-liverpool-o-mua-giai-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Liverpool 2018 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i t\u00e2n binh Fabinho v\u00e0 Naby Keita, s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a hai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng gi\u00fap kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Fabinho v\u00e0 Naby Keita \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng hy v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chi ra \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, The Kop \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ra 175 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Alisson (65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng), Naby Keita (48 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng), Fabinho (40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng), Xherdan Shaqiri (13.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Liverpool 2018 kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp th\u1ebf n\u00e0o v\u1edbi Fabinho v\u00e0 Keita h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Liverpool 2018 kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp th\u1ebf n\u00e0o v\u1edbi Fabinho v\u00e0 Keita h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool chi 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Fabinho v\u00e0 Naby Keita</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa l\u00e0 n\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Klopp \u01b0u ti\u00ean n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c khi\u1ebfn Liverpool ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 88 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Fabinho v\u00e0 Naby Keita.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Liverpool 2018 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i t\u00e2n binh Fabinho v\u00e0 Naby Keita, s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a hai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng gi\u00fap kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. Fabinho (24 tu\u1ed5i) v\u00e0 Naby Keita (23 tu\u1ed5i) \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNaby Keita l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng bao ph\u1ee7 khu gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 hay t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sung m\u00e3n, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Guinee c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111eo b\u00e1m c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Leipzig, h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111eo b\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ebfn khi \u0111o\u1ea1t l\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng di\u1ec5n ra th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Naby Keita, Fabinho c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. V\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u cao 1m88, anh c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i r\u1ea5t nhanh nh\u1eb9n v\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00e1n \u0111o\u00e1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fabinho va Naby Keita co kha nang len cong ve thu tuyet voi\" title=\"Fabinho v\u00e0 Naby Keita c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00ean c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Fabinho v\u00e0 Naby Keita c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00ean c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nFabinho l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ch\u1eb7n c\u00fa s\u00fat nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Monaco \u1edf Ligue 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Fabinho v\u00e0 Naby Keita, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1eeb xa c\u1ee7a Liverpool s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 gi\u1ea3m t\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nFabinho v\u00e0 Naby Keita c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Keita l\u00e0 m\u1ed1i \u0111e d\u1ecda th\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1ef1c v\u1edbi khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00fat xa c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, ngo\u00e0i ra ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995 c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, Naby Keita g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o 27 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Leipzig \u1edf Bundesliga (bao g\u1ed3m 14 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 13 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o). V\u1edbi Fabinho, anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 16 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i Ligue 1 trong 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng Fabinho v\u00e0 Naby Keita s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, Naby Keita \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u pha r\u00ea d\u1eaft b\u00f3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 Milner, Henderson v\u00e0 Wijnaldum c\u1ed9ng l\u1ea1i. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i&nbsp;t\u1ea1o ra 8 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Fabinho l\u00e0 7. B\u1ed9 ba James Milner (5), Henderson (2) v\u00e0 Wijnaldum (1) c\u1ee7a&nbsp;Liverpool ch\u1ec9 t\u1ea1o ra c\u00f3 8 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fabinho va Naby Keita se la trai tim cua Liverpool o mua giai toi\" title=\"Fabinho v\u00e0 Naby Keita s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u00e1i tim c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/klopp.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Fabinho v\u00e0 Naby Keita s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u00e1i tim c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNaby Keita th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1edbi 12 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ecdc khe m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, Fabinho \u0111\u1ee9ng ngay ph\u00eda sau v\u1edbi 8 l\u1ea7n, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Milner v\u00e0 Henderson ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 7, Wijnaldum th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 l\u1ea7n m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u1ecdc khe.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Fabinho v\u00e0 Keita, b\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng b\u1ebf t\u1eafc, Fabinho v\u00e0 Keita c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u00fat xa c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c r\u1ea5t cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Chamberlain \u0111ang ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u00ec Klopp c\u00f3 trong tay 6 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa, bao g\u1ed3m Fabinho, Keita, Henderson, Wijnaldum, Milner v\u00e0 Lallana.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 gi\u00e0u chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u, HLV Klopp c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u00e0 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt. \u00d4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ee7 ch\u1ed1t ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i, cho ph\u00e9p Liverpool c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ef1 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Keita v\u00e0 Fabinho s\u1ebd gi\u00fap <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/clubs/liverpool-2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool</span> c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tin v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ee7 c\u1ea3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c l\u1eabn s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1872","checkdouble":"192486"},{"date":"17:49 01/08","title":"Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/30/xuan-truong-khong-chac-suat-da-chinh-tai-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n cho bi\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng ai \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><h2>Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh CLB HAGL l\u1eabn \u1edf c\u1ea3 \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111ang l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a NHM b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i sau hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng, Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u2018h\u00edp\u2019 \u0111ang ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh t\u1eeb th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 cho t\u1edbi t\u01b0 duy ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng. L\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam song ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 HAGL v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n khi tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/xuan-truong-khong-chac-suat-da-chinh-tai-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn \u0111ang mi\u1ec7t m\u00e0i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 ASIAD</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00f3i: \"Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a b\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1edbi. Ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc ai s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc ai s\u1ebd n\u1eb1m trong danh s\u00e1ch 20 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn Indonesia s\u1eafp t\u1edbi\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh c\u0169ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0n anh ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 23 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y: \"S\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a 4 \u0111\u00e0n anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t. H\u1ecd \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao, l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u1edf CLB. Vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 c\u00e1c anh trong \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00fap b\u1ecdn em h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. C\u00e1c anh c\u0169ng s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 d\u1ea1y c\u00e1ch v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb th\u00eam v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Tuy\u00ean Quang cho r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh \u0111ang g\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat \u00e1p l\u1ef1c: \"T\u00f4i c\u00f3 g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c t\u00e2m l\u00fd. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eadp trung l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao khi\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. Ai c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng tr\u00ean 100% s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0169ng coi gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00fap Vinaphone s\u1eafp t\u1edbi l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m. \"Gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf s\u1eafp t\u1edbi l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m cho \u0111\u1ed9i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. C\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5y gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao. Ai c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c trong t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u1ee9 ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ebfn giao h\u1eefu\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y l\u00e0 U23 Palestine, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng: \"Palestine l\u00e0 v\u00ed d\u1ee5 \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018. Palestine s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh cao to, ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu U23 Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i th\u1ee9 6, 3/8. Bongda24h s\u1ebd t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hong-duy-noi-gi-sau-khi-mat-suat-du-asiad-168-192438.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/hong-duy-noi-gi-sau-khi-mat-suat-du-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hong-duy-noi-gi-sau-khi-mat-suat-du-asiad-168-192438.html\">H\u1ed3ng Duy n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi m\u1ea5t su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 ASIAD?</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Phong H\u1ed3ng Duy \u0111\u00e3 ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i chia tay \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u00e0 c\u1ea7u...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-don-them-mot-tin-xau-ve-nhan-su-168-192437.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/dt-olympic-viet-nam-don-them-mot-tin-xau-ve-nhan-su.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-don-them-mot-tin-xau-ve-nhan-su-168-192437.html\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00f3n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tin x\u1ea5u v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1</span><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Nguy\u1ec5n Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng may g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/blv-quang-huy-vtv-bi-ep-gia-do-hieu-ung-u23-viet-nam-168-192391.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/blv-quang-huy-vtv-bi-ep-gia-do-hieu-ung-u23-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/blv-quang-huy-vtv-bi-ep-gia-do-hieu-ung-u23-viet-nam-168-192391.html\">BLV Quang Huy: VTV b\u1ecb \u00e9p gi\u00e1 do hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0i truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD v\u00ec gi\u00e1 cao, b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn vi\u00ean Quang Huy cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1871","checkdouble":"192487"},{"date":"10:19 01/08","title":"Barkley quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea1i Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/barkley-quyet-tim-lai-vi-tri-o-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ross Barkley quy\u1ebft t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf Chelsea. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua c\u01a1n \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng n\u1eeda cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec1u hy v\u1ecdng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barkley g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi t\u1edbi Chelsea</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018, Chelsea quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 Ross Barkley t\u1eeb Everton. \u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, The Blues \u0111ang t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t b\u1ebf t\u1eafc. H\u1ecd thi\u1ebfu \u0111i m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n chuy\u1ec1n t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 cho Eden Hazard trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh ch\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng Alvaro Morata c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 v\u00f4 duy\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, n\u1eeda n\u0103m c\u1ee7a Barkley t\u1ea1i Chelsea tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n anh. Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng khi\u1ebfn cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 4 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho The Blues tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Trong nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u00edt \u1ecfi \u0111\u00f3, Barkley c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barkley quy\u1ebft t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barkley quy\u1ebft t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/barkley-quyet-tim-lai-vi-tri-o-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Barkley quy\u1ebft t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00ec th\u1ebf, Barkley kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi v\u00e0o \u0110T Anh d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. T\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 song s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Everton ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t \u0111i xu\u1ed1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u1ed3i sinh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 qua, Barkley quy\u1ebft t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf Chelsea. Anh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u00e0 t\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng r\u1ea5t ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i t\u1edbi Chelsea v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n&rdquo;, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1eebng 22 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T Anh n\u00f3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Arsenal t\u1ea1i International Champions Cup. &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb m\u00e0 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f2n \u1edf ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"sarri\" title=\"sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/19/cesar-azpilicueta-noi-gi-ve-hlv-sarri.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barkley c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y l\u00e3ng ph\u00ed th\u1eddi gian b\u1edfi t\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m gia nh\u1eadp h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 1 t\u1edbi nay, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y sung m\u00e3n v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u00e0 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV m\u1edbi. T\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1edbi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;&ldquo;T\u1ea1i Chelsea, t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y nh\u01b0 \u1edf nh\u00e0. HLV Sarri c\u00f3 phong c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m. S\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i h\u01a1n khi c\u00f3 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00e2ng cao, \u00e1p s\u00e1t v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt v\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ghi b\u00e0n, t\u1ea1o ra c\u00e1c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00f9ng Chelsea. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dung-bom-tien-giu-chan-nha-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-172-192430.html\">Chelsea d\u00f9ng bom ti\u1ec1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/muc-tieu-khung-cua-mu-va-chelsea-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-172-192422.html\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 100 tri\u1ec7u euro c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho MU v\u00e0 Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-chelsea-hot-nhat-ngay-3107-172-192406.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 31/07</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/antonio-conte-hai-nam-nem-trai-du-hi-no-ai-o-cung-chelsea-389-192401.html\">Antonio Conte: Hai n\u0103m n\u1ebfm tr\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee7 H\u1ec9 N\u1ed9 \u00c1i \u1ed0 c\u00f9ng Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-ly-do-khien-real-van-chua-the-cong-bo-bom-tan-courtois-172-192377.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! L\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Real v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 bom t\u1ea5n Courtois</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1870","checkdouble":"192452"},{"date":"10:34 01/08","title":"Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t si\u00eau sao chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1eddi Real \u0111\u1ebfn Serie A","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/19/inter-len-ke-hoach-chieu-mo-luka-modric.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u1edd Sky Sports \u0111\u01b0a tin Inter Milan \u0111ang li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Luka Modric \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia t\u1edbi Giuseppe Meazza ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Modric ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Modric \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i 43 tr\u1eadn cho Real Madrid m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u0103ng quang danh hi\u1ec7u Champions League th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eafm b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Croatia \u1edf World Cup 2018. Anh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n r\u00f5 n\u00e9t v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng Vatreni l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft. Nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc gi\u00fap <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-vat/luka-modric-ngon-co-dau-cua-nguoi-croatia-389-190104.html\" target=\"_blank\">Luka Modric</span> gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Inter nh\u1eafm chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Modric\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Inter mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Modric c\u1ee7a Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Inter mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Modric c\u1ee7a Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/Inter-muon-chieu-mo-Modric-cua-Real-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Inter mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Modric c\u1ee7a Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd Sky Sports, Inter \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Modric b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Nerazzurri s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i Champions League l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 6 n\u0103m \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Serie A \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 Arturo Vidal c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Real nh\u1ea3 Modric.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Inter l\u00fac n\u00e0y c\u00f3 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Modric \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia. Marcelo Brozovic, Ivan Perisic v\u00e0 Sime Vrsaljko \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho Inter \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Modric.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t si\u00eau sao l\u1edbn trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 Cristiano Ronaldo. \u201cK\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng\u201d kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u1ea5t th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1eefa nh\u01b0 Modric. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham v\u1ecdng, vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e0o tho\u00e1t l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Real Madrid:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-co-150-trieu-euro-cung-dung-mo-lewandowski-180-192443.html\">Real Madrid c\u00f3 150 tri\u1ec7u Euro c\u0169ng \u0111\u1eebng m\u01a1 Lewandowski</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/clb-real-madrid-co-dong-thai-moi-vu-hazard-180-192441.html\">CLB Real Madrid c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i m\u1edbi v\u1ee5 Hazard</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1869","checkdouble":"192453"},{"date":"10:23 01/08","title":"Man Utd c\u1ea7n th\u00eam 5 t\u00e2n binh n\u1eefa m\u1edbi m\u01a1 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/man-utd-can-them-5-tan-binh-nua-moi-mo-canh-tranh-vo-dich.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, nh\u01b0ng Jose Mourinho chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Real Madrid r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nMourinho h\u1ea1 th\u1ea5p th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec1u ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi\u1ebfu qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa M.U vs Real Madrid ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd b\u1edfi th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u, thay v\u00ec tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n cho kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft. Alexis Sanchez v\u00e0 Ander Herrera l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Karim Benzema g\u1ee1 l\u1ea1i 1 b\u00e0n cho K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 2-1, Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t Mourinho cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec c\u1ea3. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. H\u1ecd bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn, trong t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee5t l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u01b0 Herrera, Bailly, Mata, Darmian, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tinh th\u1ea7n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi thi \u0111\u00e2\u00ed m\u1ecdi ph\u00fat trong m\u1ecdi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u00ec v\u1eady trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i th\u1eafng 2-1, h\u00f2a 2-2, thua 1-2 c\u0169ng v\u1eady, ch\u1eb3ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 m\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Real Madrid\" title=\"Mourinho chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/mourinho-chien-thang-truoc-real-chang-co-y-nghia-gi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u00e1c ch\u00e0ng trai n\u00e0y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 qu\u00e1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 cho CLB v\u00ec ni\u1ec1m t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1edbi m\u00e0u \u00e1o n\u00e0y. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c khi \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 thua Real Madrid 1-6, nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, h\u1ecd th\u1eadt phi th\u01b0\u1eddng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Herrera, Mata v\u00e0 Sanchez, h\u1ecd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng l\u00e0 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb r\u1ea5t thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh trong 15 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, h\u1ecd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ebft v\u00e0 xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ecba ng\u1ee5c v\u1eabn mang theo Kroos, Asensio, Isco.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y &lsquo;xong&rsquo; r\u1ed3i, v\u00ec v\u1eady th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i gi\u00e0nh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. Nh\u01b0ng x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho Premier League, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng s\u1ed1ng s\u00f3t \u0111\u1ec3 xua tan s\u1ee9c \u00e9p trong th\u1eddi gian qua. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a g\u00ec.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;V\u1edbi Real &ndash; CLB xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i xin l\u1ed7i v\u00ec M.U kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn cho h\u1ecd m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n&rdquo; &ndash; Jose Mourinho chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-21-real-tim-lai-niem-vui-noi-cua-tu-172-192450.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/du-am-mu-21-real-tim-lai-niem-vui-noi-cua-tu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/du-am-mu-21-real-tim-lai-niem-vui-noi-cua-tu-172-192450.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m M.U 2-1 Real: T\u00ecm l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m vui n\u01a1i &ldquo;c\u1eeda t\u1eed&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t ch\u00fat n\u00e0o, ai c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 Man United s\u1ebd th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid. Nh\u01b0ng d\u01b0 \u00e2m M.U 2-1 Real \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 ra \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jose...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-mu-21-real-madrid-icc-2018-329-192449.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/video-tong-hop-mu-21-real-madrid-icc-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-mu-21-real-madrid-icc-2018-329-192449.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: MU 2-1 Real Madrid (ICC 2018)</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i ICC 2018 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Real Madrid, HLV Jose Mourinho b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh, \u00edt thay \u0111\u1ed5i nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 trong tr\u1eadn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1868","checkdouble":"192454"},{"date":"10:54 01/08","title":"B\u1ecb Mourinho th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c, d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man Utd t\u00ednh c\u1eaft ng\u1eafn k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/bi-mourinho-thuc-giuc-dan-cau-thu-man-utd-cat-ngan-ky-nghi-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Marcus Rashford, Phil Jones,... v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man Utd kh\u00e1c \u0111ang t\u00ednh c\u1eaft ng\u1eafn k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 World Cup \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 sau l\u1eddi k\u00eau g\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man Utd c\u1eaft ng\u1eafn k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 thi\u1ebfu qu\u00e2n v\u00ec c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u0111ang trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u1eadu World Cup, Jose Mourinho m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 k\u00eau g\u1ecdi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1eaft ng\u1eafn k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Theo Independent, Marcus Rashford v\u00e0 Phil Jones l\u00e0 hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u00e0y t\u1ecf th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 khi s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u1edbm.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u1ecb Mourinho th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c, d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man Utd c\u1eaft ng\u1eafn k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u1ecb Mourinho th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c, d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man Utd c\u1eaft ng\u1eafn k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/bi-mourinho-thuc-giuc-dan-cau-thu-man-utd-cat-ngan-ky-nghi-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Man Utd c\u1eaft ng\u1eafn k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 World Cup v\u00ec Mourinho.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Anh kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Ruben Loftus-Cheek c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eaft ng\u1eafn k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi t\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri. Bernardo Silva c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Man City s\u1edbm khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi hi\u1ec7u tri\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a HLV Pep Guardiola.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Man Utd c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t ch\u01b0a tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 Romelu Lukaku, Paul Pogba, Ashley Young,...<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ed7i lo v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Hi\u1ec7p h\u1ed9i C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p Anh, m\u1ed7i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n ngh\u1ec9 \"t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 5 tu\u1ea7n m\u1ed7i n\u0103m, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 3 tu\u1ea7n li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp\". Hi\u1ec7p h\u1ed9i C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi (FIFPro) b\u00e0y t\u1ecf lo ng\u1ea1i r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1eaft ng\u1eafn k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 trong n\u0103m nay s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra ti\u1ec1n l\u1ec7 x\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">FIFPro tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 lo ng\u1ea1i: \"C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n, b\u1ecb k\u1eb9t gi\u1eefa l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 v\u00e0 nhu c\u1ea7u c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. FIFPro hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Champions League v\u00e0 Europa League t\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9, s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb \u0111e d\u1ecda v\u00ec l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">FIFPro hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u00e0nh lang \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 4 tu\u1ea7n trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n gi\u1eefa tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, cho \u0111\u1ebfn bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Man Utd h\u00e8 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/man-utd-can-them-5-tan-binh-nua-moi-mo-canh-tranh-vo-dich-172-192454.html\">Man Utd c\u1ea7n th\u00eam 5 t\u00e2n binh n\u1eefa m\u1edbi m\u01a1 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-man-utd-trai-long-khi-bi-mourinho-xep-da-trai-keo-172-192380.html\">T\u00e2n binh Man Utd tr\u1ea3i l\u00f2ng khi b\u1ecb Mourinho x\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00e1i k\u00e8o</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jose-mourinho-co-nguy-co-bi-sa-thai-cao-nhat-tai-premier-league-172-192349.html\">Jose Mourinho c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i cao nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Premier League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-toi-307-jose-mourinho-cau-cuu-nhom-tru-cot-man-utd-184-192346.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 30/7: Jose Mourinho c\u1ea7u c\u1ee9u nh\u00f3m tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Man Utd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/ngay-hom-nay-307-187-192302.html\">Tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00e0y 30/7: Man Utd ch\u00e0o b\u00e1n Martial cho PSG</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jose-mourinho-tuyen-bo-khong-mua-ve-xem-man-utd-thi-dau-172-192298.html\">Jose Mourinho tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng th\u00e8m mua v\u00e9 xem Man Utd thi \u0111\u1ea5u</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1867","checkdouble":"192455"},{"date":"10:55 01/08","title":"PSG ch\u01b0a t\u1eeb b\u1ecf tham v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu sao s\u00e1ng Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/6/psg-chua-tu-bo-kante.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>PSG ch\u01b0a t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Kante, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c, Les Parisiens v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u01b0a anh h\u1ed3i h\u01b0\u01a1ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea t\u00ednh tr\u00f3i ch\u00e2n Kante</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, N'Golo Kante l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a Chelsea. Chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 32 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Leicester City, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n m\u00ecnh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 hay nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKante g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn trong 2 danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League v\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00fap FA c\u1ee7a Chelsea 2 m\u00f9a qua. M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, anh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. V\u1edbi n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c sung m\u00e3n c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tranh ch\u1ea5p tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, Kante c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 hi\u1ec7u h\u00f3a nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Lionel Messi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"PSG ch\u01b0a t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Kante, nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"PSG ch\u01b0a t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Kante, nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/PSG-chua-tu-bo-Kante,-nha-vo-dich-World-Cup-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Chelsea t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Kante</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nBi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Kante, Chelsea d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng d\u00e0nh cho anh m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 290 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n, m\u1ee9c cao k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>PSG ch\u01b0a b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c gi\u1eef ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Chelsea, PSG ch\u01b0a t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Kante. D\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 h\u1eadu thu\u1eabn c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 Qatar, \u0111\u1ea1i gia n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cuoi cung thi Kante cung duoc thoai mai tao dang voi chiec cup ma khong con phai ben len nho ban muon ho.\" title=\"Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng th\u00ec Kante c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i t\u1ea1o d\u00e1ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i b\u1ebdn l\u1ebdn nh\u1edd b\u1ea1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u1ed9.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/deschamps-can-loi-khi-kante-xuong-phong-do-o-chung-ket-world-cup.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u01b0ng PSG ch\u01b0a t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Kante, nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch WC\u00a02018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Thomas Tuchel t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 mua Kante c\u1ee7a PSG. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u00f4ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m d\u00e0nh cho nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018. H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, PSG m\u1edbi chia tay l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Thiago Motta v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Adrien Rabiot ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111ang r\u1ee5c r\u1ecbch ra \u0111i. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a Barcelona. \u1ede ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Lassana Diarra l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i th\u00ec nh\u1eefng Lo Celso hay Yacine Adli l\u1ea1i thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/clb-real-madrid-co-dong-thai-moi-vu-hazard-180-192441.html\">CLB Real Madrid c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i m\u1edbi v\u1ee5 Hazard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/muc-tieu-khung-cua-mu-va-chelsea-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-172-192422.html\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 100 tri\u1ec7u euro c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho MU v\u00e0 Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-chelsea-hot-nhat-ngay-3107-172-192406.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 31/07</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-ly-do-khien-real-van-chua-the-cong-bo-bom-tan-courtois-172-192377.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! L\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Real v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 bom t\u1ea5n Courtois</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/willian-chinh-thuc-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-mu-va-real-madrid-172-192368.html\">Willian ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho MU v\u00e0 Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1866","checkdouble":"192456"}]}